{"image_id": "KEY_2014_page_178", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Fair Values, Volume of Activity, and Gain/Loss Information Related to Derivative Instruments", "bbox": [162.5, 158.9, 1006.4, 179.7]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes the fair values of our derivative instruments on a gross and net basis as of", "bbox": [162.5, 209.1, 1050.7, 229.9]}, {"text": "December 31, 2014, and December 31, 2013. The change in the notional amounts of these derivatives by type", "bbox": [162.5, 234.1, 1079.5, 254.9]}, {"text": "from December 31, 2013, to December 31, 2014, indicates the volume of our derivative transaction activity", "bbox": [162.5, 259.1, 1060.1, 279.9]}, {"text": "during 2014. The notional amounts are not affected by bilateral collateral and master netting agreements. The", "bbox": [162.5, 284.1, 1076.8, 304.9]}, {"text": "derivative asset and liability balances are presented on a gross basis, prior to the application of bilateral collateral", "bbox": [162.5, 309.1, 1107.6, 329.9]}, {"text": "and master netting agreements. Total derivative assets and liabilities are adjusted to take into account the impact", "bbox": [162.5, 334.1, 1100.2, 354.9]}, {"text": "of legally enforceable master netting agreements that allow us to settle all derivative contracts with a single", "bbox": [162.5, 359.1, 1059.0, 379.9]}, {"text": "counterparty on a net basis and to offset the net derivative position with the related cash collateral. Where master", "bbox": [162.5, 384.1, 1105.8, 404.9]}, {"text": "netting agreements are not in effect or are not enforceable under bankruptcy laws, we do not adjust those", "bbox": [162.5, 409.1, 1037.6, 429.9]}, {"text": "derivative assets and liabilities with counterparties. Securities collateral related to legally enforceable master", "bbox": [162.5, 434.1, 1069.1, 454.9]}, {"text": "netting agreements is not offset on the balance sheet. Our derivative instruments are included in “derivative", "bbox": [162.5, 459.1, 105