.4, 1103.5, 852.9]}, {"text": "Net derivative amounts", "bbox": [212.5, 863.3, 328.9, 875.8]}, {"text": "$65,317", "bbox": [697.6, 863.2, 738.2, 875.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [770.1, 863.2, 776.4, 875.7]}, {"text": "454", "bbox": [789.9, 863.2, 808.6, 875.7]}, {"text": "$ 543", "bbox": [848.4, 863.2, 882.8, 875.7]}, {"text": "$68,077", "bbox": [916.8, 863.3, 957.4, 875.8]}, {"text": "$ 335", "bbox": [994.0, 863.3, 1023.1, 875.8]}, {"text": "$ 127", "bbox": [1070.2, 863.3, 1099.4, 875.8]}, {"text": "(a)", "bbox": [162.5, 926.8, 181.0, 943.5]}, {"text": "Netting adjustments represent the amounts recorded to convert our derivative assets and liabilities from a gross basis to a net basis in", "bbox": [195.8, 926.8, 1079.2, 943.5]}, {"text": "accordance with the applicable accounting guidance.", "bbox": [195.8, 947.7, 547.2, 964.3]}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [162.5, 981.0, 181.9, 997.7]}, {"text": "Other collateral represents the amount that cannot be used to offset our derivative assets and liabilities from a gross basis to a net basis in", "bbox": [195.8, 981.0, 1107.4, 997.7]}, {"text": "accordance with the applicable accounting guidance. The other collateral consists of securities and is exchanged under bilateral collateral", "bbox": [195.8, 1001.8, 1108.8, 1018.5]}, {"text": "and master netting agreements that allow us to offset the net derivative position with the related collateral. The application of the other", "bbox": [195.8, 1022.7, 1090.8, 1039.3]}, {"text": "collateral cannot reduce the net derivative position below zero. Therefore, excess other collateral, if any, is not reflected above.", "bbox": [195.8, 1043.5, 1041.6, 1060.2]}, {"text": "Fair value hedges. Instruments designated as fair value hedges are recorded at fair value and included in", "bbox": [162.5, 1090.1, 1043.5, 1111.2]}, {"text": "“derivative assets” or “derivative liabilities” on the balance sheet. The effective portion of a change in the fair", "bbox": [162.5, 1115.3, 1079.8, 1136.2]}, {"text": "value of an instrument designated as a fair value hedge is recorded in earnings at the same time as a change in", "bbox": [162.5, 1140.3, 1080.2, 1161.2]}, {"text": "fair value of the hedged item, resulting in no effect on net income. The ineffective portion of a change in the fair", "bbox": [162.5, 1165.3, 1101.0, 1186.2]}, {"text": "value of such a hedging instrument is recorded in “other income” on the income statement with no corresponding", "bbox": [162.5, 1190.3, 1108.9, 1211.2]}, {"text": "offset. During the year ended December 31, 2014, we did not exclude any portion of these hedging instruments", "bbox": [162.5, 1215.3, 1090.5, 1236.2]}, {"text": "from the assessment of hedge effectiveness. While there is some immaterial ineffectiveness in our hedging", "bbox": [162.5, 1240.3, 1053.8, 1261.2]}, {"text": "relationships, all of our fair value hedges remained “highly effective” as of December 31, 2014.", "bbox": [162.5, 1265.3, 961.9, 1286.2]}, {"text": "165", "bbox": [621.9, 1484.1, 653.1, 1504.9]}]}